title: 820-3476 3 Beeps not passing post
message:
Hi,
I have a 820-3476 Liquid Spill not real obvious damage. hit power button 3 beeps not passing post. Can this be U5870? (there was a little greasiness there)
Thanks,
Rick

title: 820-3476 3 Beeps not passing post
message: Check if your ram is getting power if so, Preheat the board in the oven @275 for 5 min then put lots of flux and reflow the ram. If the Ram is not getting power, Investigate that.

title: 820-3476 3 Beeps not passing post
message: Voltage on L7430? If 1V35 is ok then probably corrosion under RAM or CPU. Or someone fucked with it and knocked off component around RAM/CPU area.
